---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import { showBuyAudiobookButton, showAmazonTag, book } from "../config.json"
---

<main
	class="xl:mt-23 mx-auto mb-8 mt-12 max-w-screen-xl px-4 sm:mb-12 sm:mt-12 sm:px-6 md:mb-20 md:mt-32 xl:mb-24"
>
	<div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
		<div class="md:max-w-1xl mb-12 md:mx-auto lg:col-span-8">
			<h1
				class="mb-12 mt-1 text-4xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-10 tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl sm:leading-none lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
			>
				Food For <span class="underline">All.</span>
			</h1>
			<h2 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase">Let's Seed U.P.</h2>
			<p
				class="mb-6 mt-3 font-body text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg"
			>
				Letâ€™s Seed U.P.! is a seed distribution/garden building and support
				project funded through a grant provided by District 10.
				<a href="/hunger/services#lets-seed-up">Click for REAL details!</a>
			</p>
			<h2 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase">Emergency Food Transportation</h2>
			<p
				class="mb-6 mt-3 font-body text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg"
			>
				In an emergency situation, access to food resources is critical. The
				ability to transport food from one location to individuals and families
				in need in a community is our goal. <a
					href="/hunger/services#emergency-food-transportation"
					>Click for REAL details!</a
				>
			</p>
			<h2 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase">Kids Backpack Program</h2>
			<p
				class="mb-6 mt-3 font-body text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg"
			>
				D10 Hunger's mission is to fight against hunger by providing food &amp;
				life-changing aid. We've realized that schools are the perfect target
				for the Backpack program - they are the gathered location for children
				in need. <a href="/hunger/services#kids-backpack-program"
					>Click for REAL details!</a
				>
			</p>
			<h2 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase">
				UP Food As Medicine/UP Fresh Food Access Program
			</h2>
			<p
				class="mb-6 mt-3 font-body text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg"
			>
				...is a practice built on the knowledge that food and diet play
				important roles in disease prevention and management by prioritizing
				food and diet in an individual&#39;s health plan, with the goal of
				overall health. <a href="/hunger/services#food-as-medicine"
					>Click for REAL details!</a
				>
			</p>
			<div>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-book-gray sm:mt-5 sm:text-base">
					For any of the above, we gladly accept donations directly through this
					site!
					<a
						href="/static/(Sample)-14-Habits-of-Highly-Productive-Developers.pdf"
					>
						Please consider helping us with financial support!</a
					>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div
			id="hero-image"
			class="relative mt-12 sm:mx-auto sm:max-w-lg lg:col-span-4 lg:mx-0 lg:mt-0 lg:flex lg:max-w-none lg:items-center"
		>
		</div>
	</div>
</main>

<style>
	#hero-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: contain;
		object-position: 250px;
		background-image: url("/hunger/hero.jpg");
	}
</style>
